OL,3,CPerseid meteor shower: When and where
OL,4,Cto see up to 100 meteors every hour
OL,6,FA display of celestial fireworks is
OL,7,Fexpected to light up the night skies
OL,8,Fas the Earth passes through a cloud of
OL,9,Fcometary dust, producing up to 100
OL,10,Fmeteors every hour.
OL,12,FIf skies are clear, the Perseid meteor
OL,13,Fshower should be visible across the UK.
OL,15,FSo when and where can you see the
OL,16,Fcelestial display?
OL,18,FThe Perseid meteor shower should be
OL,19,Fvisible from around sunset on the
OL,20,Fnight of August 12 until the early
OL,21,Fhours of August 13.
