OL,3,CPerseid meteor shower: When and where
OL,4,Cto see up to 100 meteors every hour
OL,6,FAlthough they peak on the night of
OL,7,FAugust 12, Daniel Brown, associate
OL,8,Fprofessor in astronomy at Nottingham
OL,9,FTrent University, said it is worth
OL,10,Fkeeping an eye out for a secondary
OL,11,Fpeak, should it occur.
