OL,3,CPerseid meteor shower: When and where
OL,4,Cto see up to 100 meteors every hour
OL,6,F"So in addition to meteor showers not
OL,7,Fbeing a one-evening thing ` slowly
OL,8,Fincreasing and then decreasing over
OL,9,Fdays ` we might see that the most
OL,10,Factive evening might be followed by
OL,11,Fanother one a day or two later."
OL,13,FHow can you get the best view?
OL,15,FTo make the most of the meteors,
OL,16,Fexperts say observers should avoid
OL,17,Fwell-lit and built-up areas and try to
OL,18,Ffind unobstructed views.
