OL,3,CPerseid meteor shower: When and where
OL,4,Cto see up to 100 meteors every hour
OL,6,FProfessor Brown said you should look
OL,7,Ffor a place that is dark and away from
OL,8,Fdirect light.
OL,10,FHe said it will take viewers up to 30
OL,11,Fminutes to adjust to the darkness.
OL,13,F"Bring along patience, and it is best
OL,14,Fto observe a big range of the sky as
OL,15,Fmeteors will be visible all over."
OL,17,FWhat is the Perseid meteor shower?
